          <label auto.number="no" denominator="no"/>
          <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
            <text>The principal Act is amended by inserting, after <citation jurisdiction="nz">section <atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="30310" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="prov 53R" atidlm:xmlId="DLM477064" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>53R</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="extref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="30581" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM477064" atidlm:targetKey="865620" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM158107" atidlm:targetName="prov 53R" atidlm:sourceName="DLM477064" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM158054.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM53446.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Name" atidlm:value="prov" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Amend" atidlm:value="false" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Element_Context" atidlm:value="/act[1]/body[1]/prov[8]" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Element_Type" atidlm:value="prov" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Heading" atidlm:value="New section 53S inserted" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Label" atidlm:value="8" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Legislation_Id" atidlm:value="DLM53446" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Legislation_Number" atidlm:value="3" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Legislation_Title" atidlm:value="Broadcasting Amendment Act 2000" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Legislation_Year" atidlm:value="2000" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Revision_Number" atidlm:value="" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation>, the following section:</text>
            <amend>
              <prov id="DLM53462" irdnumbering="no" skeleton="no" toc="yes" xml:lang="en-NZ">
                <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">53S</label>
                <heading xml:lang="en-NZ">Te Reo Whakapuaki Irirangi to have regard to Government policy</heading>
                <prov.body>
                  <subprov skeleton="no" xml:lang="en-NZ">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">1</label>
                    <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
                      <text>When carrying out its function, duties, powers, rights, and authorities under this Act, Te Reo Whakapuaki Irirangi must comply with any direction given to it jointly by the Minister and the Minister of Maori Affairs in accordance with this section in relation to the general policy of the Government on the promotion, by means of broadcasting, of Maori language and Maori culture or the function, duties, powers, rights, and authorities of Te Reo Whakapuaki Irirangi.</text>
                    </para>
                  </subprov>
                  <subprov skeleton="no" xml:lang="en-NZ">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">2</label>
                    <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
                      <text>The Minister and the Minister of Maori Affairs may not give a direction in respect of—</text>
                      <label-para skeleton="no" xml:lang="en-NZ">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">a</label>
                        <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
                          <text>a specific programme; or</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                      <label-para skeleton="no" xml:lang="en-NZ">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">b</label>
                        <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
                          <text>the gathering or presentation of news or the preparation or presentation of current affairs programmes.</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                    </para>
                  </subprov>
                  <subprov skeleton="no" xml:lang="en-NZ">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">3</label>
                    <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
                      <text>The Minister and the Minister of Maori Affairs, acting jointly, must—</text>
                      <label-para skeleton="no" xml:lang="en-NZ">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">a</label>
                        <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
                          <text>give the direction to Te Reo Whakapuaki Irirangi by notice in writing; and</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                      <label-para skeleton="no" xml:lang="en-NZ">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">b</label>
                        <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
                          <text>as soon as practicable after giving the written notice,—</text>
                          <label-para skeleton="no" xml:lang="en-NZ">
                            <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">i</label>
                            <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
                              <text>publish a copy of it in the <emphasis style="italic">Gazette</emphasis>; and</text>
                            </para>
                          </label-para>
                          <label-para skeleton="no" xml:lang="en-NZ">
                            <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">ii</label>
                            <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
                              <text>present a copy of it to the House of Representatives.</text>
                            </para>
                          </label-para>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                    </para>
                  </subprov>
                </prov.body>
              </prov>
            </amend>
          </para>
        </subprov>
      </prov.body>
    </prov>
  </body>
